SG_INT_MBRDEV	Proportion of members of developing countries in international organizations, by organization (%)	515	Developing Regions	72.14286					WTO Annual Report 2015	"There is no established convention for the designation of ""developed"" and ""developing"" countries or areas in the United Nations system. Until a definition of developing countries is agreed, data under this indicator provisionally aggregates all countries located in ""developing regions"" for the purposes of monitoring ""developing countries""." Until a definition of developing countries is agreed, data under this indicator provisionally aggregates all countries located in ""developing regions"" for the purposes of monitoring ""developing countries""."
